ergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/15833/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Dostarlimab, Amivantamab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Pembrolizumab, More', 1767369485);
